{"tid":1188064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸人/新移民真係死不足惜","createTime":"2019-06-06T04:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T07:04:10.000Z","uid":181257,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"16bf4836f4eacaa502664b6fbe67c52ecfe27e5a","tid":1188064,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:35:37.000Z","msg":"無教養，無禮貌，無文化，任何地方大聲喧嘩，周圍大小二便，排隊打尖我都算。而家住嗰度越黎越多大陸人，搭shuttle bus 落車，落車次序應該係前到後，排隊有秩序落，小學生都識啦。<br />\n<br />\n條新移民八婆一到站就迫迫迫，如果係趕時間我都算，但係全程係講電話傾計，最仆街係我老婆大住肚，俾佢迫到撞到個肚一下，雖然唔係好嚴重，我即刻問佢：大陸厘你迫嘜春，大陸無教排隊？<br />\n<br />\n條八婆之後仲要一路落車一路用唔咸唔淡嘅廣東話大聲話野，但我一句都聽唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明白就算外國人都會有仆街，但以比例黎講，大陸撚屌比率應該係1:1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced38b081618dd403e7d24e343814608e7de2552","tid":1188064,"uid":181257,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T05:23:40.000Z","msg":"仲話挑戰美國<br />\n自己國民都未教好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcda34ff03a4f752d261edd7ea57678697dad26b","tid":1188064,"uid":63206,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:11:01.000Z","msg":"無接受過教育真係好可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a782a22e3cc442f63a33f978f5729ebb7295efa0","tid":1188064,"uid":181257,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fcda34ff03a4f752d261edd7ea57678697dad26b","tid":1188064,"uid":63206,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:11:01.000Z","msg":"無接受過教育真係好可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"無書讀唔係錯事，<br />\n但身教好重要，最怕係一代傳一代<br />\n大陸人我已經死心，<br />\n我最怕係新移民嘅細路會荼毒香港小朋友。"},{"pid":"cb69b18f8c79f926c2ae20a4d2fa88f0b797bd5f","tid":1188064,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:34:42.000Z","msg":"文革+六四將99%嘅支那好人殺乾殺淨，連同傳統中國嘅佛教&amp;儒家所謂仁義禮智，全部掃入歷史墳墓之中"},{"pid":"fdd9e242bfc102fe7ff633dea50aa9be5a433152","tid":1188064,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb69b18f8c79f926c2ae20a4d2fa88f0b797bd5f","tid":1188064,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:34:42.000Z","msg":"文革+六四將99%嘅支那好人殺乾殺淨，連同傳統中國嘅佛教&amp;儒家所謂仁義禮智，全部掃入歷史墳墓之中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:41:34.000Z","msg":"岩！中國人唔好好學習中國歷史，<br />\n對內恃強凌弱，對外一味靠嚇。<br />\n浪費了幾百年嘅承傳！"},{"pid":"327ab560b75dc9a7b43ef9471ff327c66a0edad8","tid":1188064,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"垃圾北佬有咩傳承可言？"},{"pid":"581769aaea69c4192807ad6bb8262a480ce51743","tid":1188064,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"327ab560b75dc9a7b43ef9471ff327c66a0edad8","tid":1188064,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"垃圾北佬有咩傳承可言？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:03:15.000Z","msg":"我覺得每段歷史都有它值得學習嘅地方，<br />\n學到前人的知識和處事也算傳承一種，<br />\n但如果唔好好學習不得止，仲要搞破壞，又迫人學習自己嗰套，要人當佢神咁拜。<br />\n<br />\n咁就注定失敗！只係時間問題"},{"pid":"75098f3a5ce5a8f14ac4c5de2ed459007d54d4b2","tid":1188064,"uid":234089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"581769aaea69c4192807ad6bb8262a480ce51743","tid":1188064,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"327ab560b75dc9a7b43ef9471ff327c66a0edad8","tid":1188064,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T06:50:28.000Z","msg":"垃圾北佬有咩傳承可言？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:03:15.000Z","msg":"我覺得每段歷史都有它值得學習嘅地方，<br />\n學到前人的知識和處事也算傳承一種，<br />\n但如果唔好好學習不得止，仲要搞破壞，又迫人學習自己嗰套，要人當佢神咁拜。<br />\n<br />\n咁就注定失敗！只係時間問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ODeW8a1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FODeW8a1.gif&h